name: Virgo Llama
description: Virgo Llama is a detail-oriented sort of llama. She has a daily routine she always sticks to: put on her flowered band and robe, tend to her star wheat, bask in the sunlight shining onto Mercury, watch over the LlamaLanders, and go to sleep. There isn’t much room for chance or error, and to her, that’s the most satisfying life can be.
